    "faq_title": "FAQ",
    "faq_q0": "Is the HodlAI API stable? What's the upstream?",
    "faq_a0": "✅ Stable & reliable! Currently using OpenAI, OpenRouter as upstream, all through official channels. Pricing matches official rates. Found discrepancies? Contact us to fix.",
    "faq_q1": "Is signing safe?",
    "faq_a1": "✅ Completely safe! Signing only verifies wallet ownership. No on-chain transaction, no Gas fee. Tokens always stay in your wallet.",
    "faq_q2": "How is the 3% tax used?",
    "faq_a2": "Prioritizes AI API funding. Holders share daily free quota by holding value. Surplus for buyback & burn or marketing. Team takes 0%.",
    "faq_q3": "How is quota calculated?",
    "faq_a3": "Formula: Daily quota = Holding ÷ $10 × $1 × Price Ratio × Release Ratio. Price ratio adjusts dynamically ($0.001=100%, $0.02=30%), release ratio increases with holding time (10% after 5min, 100% at 24h).",
    "faq_q4": "What is dynamic price ratio?",
    "faq_a4": "To protect low-price holders: 100% ratio at ≤$0.001, 30% at ≥$0.02, linear transition between. Calculated by $0.001 tiers, only recalculates when crossing tiers.",
    "faq_q5": "What if quota runs out?",
    "faq_a5": "① Wait for daily reset at 00:00 (UTC+8) ② Buy more tokens ③ Become Diamond Hands for 100% release ratio",
    "faq_q6": "What is Diamond Hands?",
    "faq_a6": "💎 Never sold/transferred + 24h holding = Diamond Hands, 100% release ratio. Max 80% if ever sold. 30min cooldown after selling. On-chain verified.",
    "faq_q7": "Is my conversation data safe?",
    "faq_a7": "🔒 Absolute privacy! We commit to never logging, storing, or analyzing any conversation data. All requests are forwarded directly to upstream APIs with zero records kept on our servers. Your privacy is fully protected.",

